    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip rear differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis is tightened with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring sharp turn-in and minimal body roll. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain robust. A purist\u2019s specification for those who prioritize tactile feedback and engineering excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
