      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with regular highway commuting. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats remain supple with minimal bolstering wear, and all electronic features\u2014from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is robust and has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule. It recently received a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a multi-point inspection. The tires boast significant tread life, and the engine runs smoothly and quietly without any persistent dashboard lights. It drives straight and true, offering a refined experience for its next owner. Full service records are available to provide complete peace of mind.",
